data.description: Better than a new build! This breath taking 2013 home has all of the amenities and more than you've been dreaming of.  From the light airy feel with new paint throughout the open spacious main floor to the gorgeous countertops and backsplash.  Don't forget about the hidden pantry to store all of the kitchen items.  The Instagram worthy living room with fireplace and spacious master bed/bath are also highlights.  The lower lever is perfect for a large family or a house full of guests.  With 3 beds/2 full baths everyone has their own space.  Large open space with projection screen and all new luxury SCP flooring.  Enjoy the beautiful sunsets on the covered lanai over looking the pool.  Oversized heated garage and shop are are a bonus too. Call or text myself or your favorite realtor to view. This home is a must see!
